{"id": 5894, "title": "Ticket #5894: Add IPv6 address to host based security meta-knob", "description": "<blockquote>\nThe host-based security meta-knob sets\n\n<p></p><div class=\"code\">\n<pre class=\"code\">ALLOW_WRITE=$(FULL_HOSTNAME) $(IP_ADDRESS)\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>$(IP_ADDRESS) expands to the ipv4 address.  In a machine with ipv6, and dns not set up, the ALLOW_WRITE won't allow local connections.  We should add the IPV6 address to ALLOW_WRITE.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Sep-13 10:06</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/4f93a55ace5bb2cda5cc058dd047cb4091c45f66\">[49176]</a></span>: Documetn <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5894\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5894'); return false;\" title=\"Add IPv6 address to host based security meta-knob\">#5894</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Sep-13 10:04</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/884e5ef4f78f828e075aa4371da9e19f6fd925ee\">[49175]</a></span>: Add ipv6 address to default host based security meta knob <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5894\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5894'); return false;\" title=\"Add IPv6 address to host based security meta-knob\">#5894</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"